sentences: Kathrin Kohlhepp (born 1988), known by her artistic name DJane HouseKat, is a German female singer, DJ and musician specializing in electronic techno music.
She became internationally famous for her 2012 dance hit "My Party", featuring British rapper Rameez.
Released in January 2012, it soon caught up in all night venues and has charted in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, and the Scandinavian countries.
